<subSubSection lastPageId="31" lastPageNumber="32" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1436,1969,2033]" lastBlockId="29.[151,1436,152,2025]" lastPageId="29" lastPageNumber="30" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1969,1996]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Distribution</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation box="[313,398,1970,1996]" captionStart="FIGURE 24" captionStartId="31.[151,250,1356,1381]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,409,1337]" captionTargetId="figure@31.[151,1436,409,1337]" captionTargetPageId="31" captionText="FIGURE 24. Records of Xanthagrion erythroneurum." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3342289/files/figure.png" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Fig. 24</figureCitation>
). This is a monotypic genus, with a widespread distribution, from 
<collectingCountry box="[1145,1254,1970,1996]" name="Indonesia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Indonesia</collectingCountry>
to most of 
<collectingCountry name="Australia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Australia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[262,301,2006,2032]" name="Fiji" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Fiji</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Tsuda, S." box="[315,451,2006,2032]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" refId="ref36559" refString="Tsuda, S. (2000) A distributional list of world Odonata. Osaka, Japan, 430 pp." type="book" year="2000">Tsuda 2000</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[498,673,2006,2033]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
, it has been recorded from five localities only in the south of Grande Terre. One specimen was collected in Nouméa (
<bibRefCitation author="Kimmins, D." box="[686,856,152,179]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" pagination="241 - 257" refId="ref33386" refString="Kimmins, D. (1953) Miss L. E. Cheesman's expedition to New Caledonia, 1949. Orders Odonata, Neuroptera and Trichoptera. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series 12, 6 (64), 241 - 257. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222935308654420" type="journal article" year="1953">Kimmins 1953</bibRefCitation>
) and another in the Montagne des Sources, both are in the 
<collectionCode box="[218,297,189,215]" country="New Caledonia" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/crvj-94ys" name="Office de la Recherche Scientifique et Technique d'Outre-Mer" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">ONNC</collectionCode>
collection. 
<bibRefCitation author="Davies, D. A. L." box="[426,585,189,215]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" pagination="229 - 251" refId="ref31736" refString="Davies, D. A. L. (2002) The odonate fauna of New Caledonia, including the descriptions of a new species and a new subspecies. Odonatologica, 31, 229 - 251." type="journal article" year="2002">Davies (2002)</bibRefCitation>
reported to have observed this species all over the island in 1979, 1981, 
<date pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="1983" valueMax="1984">1983 and 1984</date>
, but did not give the localities where he observed it.
</paragraph>
